    <node id="&quot;PROJECT GUTENBERG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Project Gutenberg is a digital library offering a collection of electronic works that are freely available. It promotes the free distribution of electronic works and is known for having a robust trademark policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Project Gutenberg is a digital library offering free access to eBooks, primarily those in the public domain, supported by volunteers and employees for copyright research, transcription, and proofreading."&lt;SEP&gt;"Project Gutenberg is a volunteer-driven digital library offering free access to a vast collection of eBooks, including classic literature like 'A Christmas Carol'."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-af4ae173c561e4594c5aea96198cce9d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-194cd9680f4967f48bea89678f7ece21</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;UNITED STATES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The United States is a country in North America where this eBook is freely available under the Project Gutenberg License."&lt;SEP&gt;"The United States is a country mentioned in the context of copyright law and the distribution of Project Gutenberg works."&lt;SEP&gt;"The United States is mentioned as part of a financial security context in Scrooge's thoughts, representing stability and standard value."&lt;SEP&gt;"The United States is mentioned in the context of copyright laws affecting the distribution and use of Project Gutenberg eBooks."&lt;SEP&gt;"The United States is where the Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation operates, subject to federal and state laws regarding non-profit organizations and charitable donations."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-af4ae173c561e4594c5aea96198cce9d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85f77f5e3a9aba01133555a2d20e2fd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-194cd9680f4967f48bea89678f7ece21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7b10789a9cb0af6c553730b29bd9034</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHARLES DICKENS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Charles Dickens is a renowned English author known for his works of literature, including 'A Christmas Carol'."&lt;SEP&gt;"Charles Dickens is the author of A Christmas Carol, a classic novel that is available in the Project Gutenberg collection."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-194cd9680f4967f48bea89678f7ece21</data>
