      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE PARROT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Parrot is a character from 'Robinson Crusoe' that Scrooge remembers fondly, showing the nostalgia for stories of adventure and survival."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ROBIN CRUSOE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Robin Crusoe, a reference to Robinson Crusoe, is part of the stories that provided Scrooge with imaginative journeys during his lonely moments."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SCROOGE'S FORMER SELF&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
