      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SPIRIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Spirit is a guiding figure in the text, showing Scrooge scenes from his past to evoke reflection and emotional growth."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Spirit is a supernatural and guiding entity that takes Scrooge on a journey to observe different Christmas celebrations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Spirit is a supernatural entity accompanying Scrooge, spreading joy and mirth during the holiday season."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Spirit refers to the supernatural entity that Scrooge addresses, expressing his realization and fear of his own potential future."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1f29eeadc1d8ab46dc8a0bbd3c56b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91614df5cb74cbe5e109a338a82041e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE LITTLE GIRL&quot;">
