      <data key="d1">"The Spirit's Glance refers to the moment when Scrooge feels the weight of the Ghost’s presence and reconsideration of his past choices."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHRISTMAS PAST&quot;">
