      <data key="d2">chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;A GOLDEN IDOL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A Golden Idol symbolizes wealth and materialism, representing the reason for the drift between Scrooge and The Fair Young Girl."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GAIN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Gain refers to Scrooge's focus on accumulating wealth, which becomes his primary concern, affecting his relationships and personal values."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GHOST&quot;">
