      <data key="d1">"The Ghost is a spectral figure guiding Scrooge through visions related to death and the consequences of a man's life, acting as a catalyst for Scrooge's transformation."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is an ethereal figure guiding Scrooge through scenes that reflect on his past decisions and their consequences."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
