      <data key="d1">"The comely matron is the young girl from Scrooge’s past, now grown and surrounded by her joyful family."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DAUGHTER OF THE COMELY MATRON&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The daughter of the comely matron who mingles playfully with her siblings and enjoys the family’s celebration."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d</data>
