    <node id="&quot;THE CRATCHIT FAMILY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Cratchit Family consists of Bob, Mrs. Cratchit, and their children, who celebrate Christmas together despite their modest means."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Cratchit Family is a close-knit family who gather for Christmas dinner and cherish each other's company despite their modest means."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Cratchit Family is a close-knit group celebrating Christmas modestly yet joyfully."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Cratchit Family, led by Bob and Mrs. Cratchit, consists of loving and supportive members who value each other greatly."</data>
