    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CHRISTMAS DAY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Christmas Day is a significant event in the narrative, marking Scrooge's realization that he hasn't missed the celebration and still has time to make amends."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas Day is a significant holiday, depicted as a time for joy, reflection, and communal celebration."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas Day is the central event around which the various entities reflect and celebrate in their own ways during the narrative."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas Day is the event during which the Cratchit family gathers to celebrate together, highlighting family and unity."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas Day is the occasion upon which the Cratchit family gathers and celebrates, despite their financial struggles."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b0f459f5af1c3a5e0b92cbe4ee48b77b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90b95db5c53e4364a6bee36b7aa4d70f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91614df5cb74cbe5e109a338a82041e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e2e7ebcc19a53b399dc03aded4743e7</data>
