    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DEATH&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Death is depicted in the text as the end that the deceased man has met, serving as a powerful theme of mortality and consequence for Scrooge."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e1f29eeadc1d8ab46dc8a0bbd3c56b64</data>
    </node>
