      <data key="d2">chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CRATCHIT'S WIFE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Cratchit's Wife is Bob Cratchit's spouse, who experiences emotional distress after the death of their child, Tiny Tim."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cratchit's wife, also known as Mrs. Cratchit, is recognized for her hard work and is admired by Bob and their children."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-1d4b58de5429cd1261370c231c8673e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
