      <data key="d1">"The girls in the Cratchit family are industrious and help with family duties, as well as share in grieving Tiny Tim."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-1d4b58de5429cd1261370c231c8673e8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BOB&quot;">
