      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ebenezer Scrooge's Grave is a pivotal future vision that symbolizes Scrooge's potential end and catalyzes his change in behavior."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SPIRIT OF TINY TIM&quot;">
