    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE POULTERER'S MAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The poulterer's man is responsible for delivering the turkey ordered by Scrooge, highlighting the logistical aspect of Scrooge's generosity."&lt;SEP&gt;"The poulterer's man is responsible for delivering the turkey ordered by Scrooge."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8f738cb25d60a7dab782162d9d0a25ed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE PORTLY GENTLEMAN&quot;">
