      <data key="d3">18.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Fezziwig and Mrs. Fezziwig are partners in both marriage and dance, contributing to the success and warmth of the Christmas Eve Party."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig and Mrs. Fezziwig host the dance together, demonstrating their partnership and shared role in spreading happiness."</data>
