      <data key="d3">6.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Phantom with Iron Safe is part of the group of The Ghosts that Scrooge observes, illustrating the eternal burden of their earthly lives."</data>
      <data key="d5">chunk-cb661c37436355ccec2769b1d0350c5f</data>
      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
