      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;SPIRIT&quot;" target="&quot;SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">35.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Scrooge is accompanied by the Spirit, who shows him scenes and teaches him lessons about his past, present, and future."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge is guided by the Spirit as they observe and reflect on the holiday spirit and goodwill among people."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Spirit compels Scrooge to witness scenes of his past, causing him to reflect on his life choices."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Spirit, as the Ghost of Christmas Present, is guiding Scrooge through experiences meant to teach him valuable lessons about joy and generosity."</data>
      <data key="d5">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843b5b2f944c7413d9ca876e2e2f151f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02baee20cc9463dbe08170a8e1043e32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0f459f5af1c3a5e0b92cbe4ee48b77b</data>
