      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Spirit spreads joy and brightens the atmosphere during the Cratchit family's Christmas celebrations."</data>
      <data key="d5">chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b</data>
      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;THE SPIRIT&quot;" target="&quot;THE STREET&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Spirit celebrates the joyous atmosphere of the street during Christmastime, enhancing its brightness and liveliness."</data>
