    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;THE SPIRIT&quot;" target="&quot;THE SHIP'S CREW&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Spirit leads Scrooge to witness the ship's crew embracing Christmas spirit at sea, revealing universal festive connections."</data>
